The 2018 MyBroadband Cloud Conference has kicked off at the Gallagher Convention Centre in Midrand. The conference is brought to delegates in partnership with Liquid Telecom, with the company’s CEO Reshaad Sha delivering the keynote address. Speakers at the conference include Connection Telecom’s Sacha Matulovich, Amazon Web Services’ Michael Needham, Microsoft’s Joachim Hammer, and Google Cloud Partner Siatik’s Brett StClair. Delegates will also be treated to excellent exhibitions from South Africa’s top cloud and telecoms providers, including Connection Telecom, Axiz, Microsoft, and SITA. The conference has attracted over 1,500 IT executives from across South Africa and neighbouring countries. A look at the 2018 MyBroadband Cloud Conference, and what delegates are treated to, is shown below.            